                  watchdog_enable PROC
;;;11012  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;11013  void watchdog_enable (void)

;;;11014  {
;;;11015  LPC_WDT->WDTC=2000000;

;;;11018  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;

;;;11019  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0x55;

;;;11020  }

;;;11021  
                          ENDP

                  watchdog_reset PROC
;;;11022  //-----------------------------------------------
;;;11023  void watchdog_reset (void)

;;;11025  LPC_WDT->WDFEED=0xaa;

;;;11027  }

;;;11028  
                          ENDP
